description: Loads a vector cube as part of a batch job. Vector cubes can be stored with save_vector_cube before.

parameters.description: The job-id to load the vector cube from.
parameters.name: job_id

parameters.description: The url to load the vector cube from.
parameters.name: URL

returns.description: Returns `false` if the process failed to store the vector cube, `true` otherwise.

summary: Load a vector cube from a batch job or from a URL.
